1. Create home.html, link it to ViewProductServlet.java, customize the link for each product to be added
2. Create Product.java
3. Create an in-memory DB.java to store products
4. Create ShowProductServlet, link it to AddToCartServlet
5. Create AddToCartServlet, use Session to store the product to be added
- Use the following to create/retrieve the current shopping cart.
    Map<String, Product> map = (Map<String, Product>) request.getSession().getAttribute("cart");
- Determine if a product already exists in the cart.

6. Create ViewCartServlet, use getAttribute method to get the data stored in Session


